Specifically for import status:

- Running ‚Üí `"‚è≥ Import still running ‚Äî N% complete; check back in ~M minutes."`
- Complete ‚Üí `"‚úì Import complete ‚Äî N imported ¬∑ P pending crawl ¬∑ Q need attention."` (partition `not_imported` as in the render block below; `uncrawled` rows are **pending crawl**, not failures ‚Äî drop any zero segment).
- Error / failed ‚Üí `"‚öÝ Import failed: <error>. See leadbay_resolve_import_rows for diagnosis."` ‚Äî reserve this ONLY for a true transport/backend error on the import itself, never for `uncrawled` rows inside an otherwise-complete import.

